{"tid":1570412,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"港鐵：不會主動公開8.31閉路電視錄影","createTime":"2019-09-15T05:18:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-15T05:31:50.000Z","uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f57bf069ac611f62a05eb87cf0dc738b75f1e349","tid":1570412,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:18:50.000Z","msg":"港鐵行政總裁金澤培表示，港鐵面對風險增加，已增加不少人手，並已成立特遣隊打擊違反《港鐵附例》行為。<span style=\"color: red;\">他重申除非法庭指示，否則不會主動公開8.31閉路電視錄影</span>。<br />\n<br />\n示威者連日針對港鐵車站的破壞，金澤培出席無綫節目《講清講楚》時稱，<span style=\"color: red;\">面對跳閘等違例行為，會安排包括尼泊爾裔保安等組成的200人特遣隊處理，治安問題則由警方負責</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他表示，近月發生的事，是港鐵過去40年來前所未有，暴力及破壞不斷升級，港鐵的應對方法亦要不斷改變，例如站內發生打鬥、破壞等違法行為，列車會不停站或關閉車站，以免將新的乘客帶到有關的港鐵站。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，港鐵使命是提供安全可靠的鐵路服務，令香港持續運作，不論情況有多艱難，港鐵都會盡可能維持服務。<br />\n<br />\n對於8月31日太子站事件是否公開閉路電視片段，他指出，<span style=\"color: red;\">據他了解，警方正在做調查工作，亦不相信應由港鐵單方面發放這些訊息，影響調查工作</span>。所有有資格的團體，他們通過法律，實在可以取得這些錄影，例如<span style=\"color: red;\">警方通過手令，已取了這些錄影的複製檔</span>。<br />\n<br />\n他又稱，最近港鐵客量減少，是因社會爭議影響公眾外出意欲，會透過解說和做好服務，爭取信任。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2250647/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2250647%2F&d=xWOcOck8MQRdM6xM79L4mApem%2F37D4MqEuHX91B%2FZbc%3D&h=ea35273a\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2250647/</a>"},{"pid":"a6d029c62420ba1ceb14d7b0d4eb0697e261b3be","tid":1570412,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1bf3888fb8bc2fcda830d4d34ed709c792ad22","tid":1570412,"uid":297997,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:05.000Z","msg":"但會自己比黑警<br />\n屌你老母金澤培"},{"pid":"84d32de6aec49293a37cdc46c75be4df3993dfe4","tid":1570412,"uid":209468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca320a901884517835327368aa5e1912fad04ff7","tid":1570412,"uid":194914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"點先可以令法庭做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e06d43dc06943668da8b09f5bafde7be2e003d","tid":1570412,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8eaad2381e0a8fbc48590d870431726885144035","tid":1570412,"uid":74155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:21:27.000Z","msg":"今日記得清算黨鐵<br />\ncwb wc ctrl..."},{"pid":"129b40d43c205128a919c2304efaed1ac8d6bbae","tid":1570412,"uid":15259,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:21:48.000Z","msg":"2點半銅鑼灣東角道<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n只有一個方法可以有效打擊藍屍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1570141\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1570141</a>"},{"pid":"2f595bd7798e2753a15940475a7126badf2041ad","tid":1570412,"uid":276393,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:22:36.000Z","msg":"吊你老味<br />\n死狗鐵"},{"pid":"f6103b1acaca902fb47fc3788d0bd9451dc6b5d6","tid":1570412,"uid":175091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:24:24.000Z","msg":"飯民唔係已經同831手足告緊佢地 要求拎cctv？"},{"pid":"5a2dd41a8690afe69eac7bd9c85ae4855d30b333","tid":1570412,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca320a901884517835327368aa5e1912fad04ff7","tid":1570412,"uid":194914,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:20:31.000Z","msg":"點先可以令法庭做野<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-15T05:24:48.000Z","msg":"教大學生會會長入稟高院要求港鐵披露 聽日開庭審<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/smile.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"